Package: libvdpau-sunxi1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Multi-Arch: same
Description: VDPAU implementation for sunxi SoCs
 It supports decoding of MPEG1 and MPEG2, some limited MPEG4 types,
 H.264 and on H3/A64 it also decodes H.265.

Package: libvdpau-sunxi1-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends:
 libump (= ${binary:Version}),
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: VDPAU implementation for sunxi SoCs (development files)
 It supports decoding of MPEG1 and MPEG2, some limited MPEG4 types,
 H.264 and on H3/A64 it also decodes H.265. This package is need to build
 against libvdpau-sunxi.
